WEBVTT

00:01:20.946 --> 00:01:22.626
KEN.

00:01:22.626 --> 00:01:24.129
vi heyst ir, BEVAKASHA?

00:01:24.129 --> 00:01:25.350
RAKHEL.

00:01:25.350 --> 00:01:27.338
nokh eyn, MASH- familye nomen.

00:01:26.455 --> 00:01:30.771
RAKHEL BRAUDE, geborene Pumpianski.

00:01:30.771 --> 00:01:33.666
vos far a datum zent ir geboyrn?

00:01:33.666 --> 00:01:36.315
dem f- fuftsntn in akhtn

00:01:36.315 --> 00:01:38.962
in toyznt nayn hundert tsvantsik.

00:01:38.560 --> 00:01:40.508
vifl yor hot ir yetst?

00:01:40.508 --> 00:01:43.017
yetst hob ikh zeks un zibetsik yor.

00:01:43.017 --> 00:01:45.276
in vos far a shtot un a land zent ir geboyrn?

00:01:45.034 --> 00:01:48.684
in Vilne, es gehert tsu Poyln.

00:01:48.684 --> 00:01:51.017
atsind heybn mir on di intervyu.

00:01:51.017 --> 00:01:53.543
heybt on tsu dertseyln vos ir gedenkt

00:01:53.543 --> 00:01:55.999
ven ir zent geven a kind

00:01:55.999 --> 00:02:01.157
di ershte zikhroynes.

00:02:01.157 --> 00:02:04.455
di ershte ZICHRONOT, ikh bin geven a kind.

00:02:04.455 --> 00:02:07.402
ikh bin geven di yingste in shtub.

00:02:07.402 --> 00:02:10.964
ikh hob gehat a shvester mit tsvelf yor elter

00:02:10.964 --> 00:02:12.701
un a bruder

00:02:12.701 --> 00:02:16.823
mit tsen yor, mit, tsen yor elter.

00:02:16.823 --> 00:02:19.192
vos gedenkt ir di ershte zakhn?

00:02:19.192 --> 00:02:22.298
di ershte zakh gedenk ikh

00:02:22.298 --> 00:02:26.491
az kleynerheyt, ikh bin geven a kleyne kind fun fir finf yor.

00:02:26.491 --> 00:02:26.929
yo.

00:02:26.929 --> 00:02:29.263
ikh geven zeyer a sheyne kind

00:02:29.263 --> 00:02:30.122
yo.

00:02:30.122 --> 00:02:33.929
un ikh fleg zikh arumdreyen mit ale kinder oyfn hoyf.

00:02:33.929 --> 00:02:37.859
s'hot gevoynt oyfn hoyf a shokhnte oyfn ershtn shtok

00:02:37.859 --> 00:02:39.403
a kristin

00:02:39.403 --> 00:02:41.841
vos zi hot keyn kinder nit gehat.

00:02:41.841 --> 00:02:43.753
kinderloz.

00:02:43.753 --> 00:02:46.244
hot zi bamerkt eyn mol

00:02:46.244 --> 00:02:49.192
az ikh trink fun di shmutsike vaser

00:02:49.192 --> 00:02:51.893
vos geyt aroys.

00:02:51.893 --> 00:02:54.069
un zi hot dos

00:02:54.069 --> 00:02:55.964
dertseylt mayn eltern

00:02:55.964 --> 00:02:58.350
ober leyder shoyn geven tsu shpet.

00:02:58.350 --> 00:03:02.314
ikh bin krank gevorn oyf a boykh tifus.

00:03:02.314 --> 00:03:04.262
kh'hob farlorn dem loshn

00:03:04.262 --> 00:03:06.718
kh'hob nit gekent reydn.

00:03:06.718 --> 00:03:08.525
esn hob ikh

00:03:08.525 --> 00:03:10.806
nit gevolt esn, ober

00:03:10.806 --> 00:03:14.244
mir hobn shtendik gehat in shtub a kats.

00:03:14.244 --> 00:03:17.439
ir zent geven alt fir yor ven ir zent geven krank tifus?

00:03:17.439 --> 00:03:17.999
KEN.

00:03:18.034 --> 00:03:20.122
fun trinken fun di shmutsike vaser.

00:03:20.132 --> 00:03:20.746
UNK

00:03:21.526 --> 00:03:25.999
hobn mir gehat in shtub a kats, ale mol a kats.

00:03:25.999 --> 00:03:30.157
fleg ikh heysn mayn foter mit di hent; reydn hob ikh nit gekent

00:03:30.157 --> 00:03:32.403
er zol nemen a meser

00:03:32.403 --> 00:03:35.087
avekshteln di kats oyfn tish

00:03:35.087 --> 00:03:37.947
oyfshnaydn ir di boykh

00:03:37.947 --> 00:03:39.859
un aroysnemen di esn.

00:03:39.859 --> 00:03:42.596
fun boykh, az er vet aroysnemen di esn

00:03:42.596 --> 00:03:46.631
ersht dan vil ikh esn.

00:03:46.631 --> 00:03:49.999
dos iz mayne erinerungen.

00:03:49.999 --> 00:03:52.200
oyb ir vilt nokh ken

00:03:51.438 --> 00:03:53.736
un vifl tsayt hot ir nisht geredt?

00:03:53.736 --> 00:03:57.034
ikh gleyb az lang hob ikh nit geredt.

00:03:57.034 --> 00:03:58.631
yorn?

00:03:58.631 --> 00:04:00.526
neyn.

00:04:00.526 --> 00:04:04.999
az ikh bin gezunt gevorn hob ikh genumen reydn.

00:04:04.999 --> 00:04:07.642
 ir hot gezogt ir hot gehat a shvester un a bruder.

00:04:07.438 --> 00:04:08.104
ye.

00:04:08.104 --> 00:04:09.490
vi azoy hobn zey geheysn?

00:04:09.490 --> 00:04:12.385
Mere un Leybe.

00:04:12.385 --> 00:04:15.367
Miryam Arye.

00:04:13.671 --> 00:04:14.351
yo

00:04:15.367 --> 00:04:18.350
vos gedenkt ir fun zey?

00:04:18.350 --> 00:04:20.718
vos gedenk ikh fun zey?

00:04:20.718 --> 00:04:26.893
mir hobn spetsyel, keyn, keyn spetsyele bading- nit gehat keyn eynem mit di andere

00:04:26.893 --> 00:04:29.367
a noente batsiung.

00:04:29.367 --> 00:04:32.613
vayl ven zi iz geven akhtsn

00:04:32.613 --> 00:04:34.982
bin ikh geven

00:04:34.982 --> 00:04:37.385
tsvelf. neyn; zi iz geven akhtsn

00:04:37.385 --> 00:04:38.886
bin ikh geven tsen yor.

00:04:38.754 --> 00:04:40.245
yo.

00:04:40.245 --> 00:04:43.929
un der bruder iz geven tsvantsik.

00:04:43.929 --> 00:04:47.052
ikh fleg zikh merstnteyl fleg ikh zikh farnemen

00:04:47.052 --> 00:04:48.841
mit di eltern.

00:04:48.841 --> 00:04:51.912
mitn foter fleg ikh umetum geyn.

00:04:51.912 --> 00:04:55.052
mitn foter fleg geyn oyf KADUR REGEL.

00:04:55.052 --> 00:04:56.493
vi azoy hot geheysn der foter?

00:04:56.263 --> 00:04:59.017
MIKHAEL.

00:04:59.017 --> 00:05:02.280
shabes fleg ikh mitn foter geyn oyfn KADUR REGEL.

00:05:02.280 --> 00:05:03.964
vayl mayn muter

00:05:03.964 --> 00:05:06.157
iz geven tsufridn

00:05:06.157 --> 00:05:08.218
az er nemt mir aroys fun shtub.

00:05:08.157 --> 00:05:10.175
un in shul zent ir gegangen shabes?

00:05:10.175 --> 00:05:11.157
in shul?

00:05:11.157 --> 00:05:12.771
in shul, shul.

00:05:12.771 --> 00:05:14.774
shul oyf yidish.

00:05:13.788 --> 00:05:15.648
shul, BET KNESET.

00:05:15.648 --> 00:05:18.109
shul zogt men bay undz. neyn.

00:05:16.977 --> 00:05:17.509
shul.

00:05:17.964 --> 00:05:18.565
neyn.

00:05:18.420 --> 00:05:22.981
in shul bin ikh nor gegangen mit di eltern

00:05:22.981 --> 00:05:24.438
di yontoyvim.

00:05:24.242 --> 00:05:25.149
yo.

00:05:25.736 --> 00:05:27.911
mer nit.

00:05:28.143 --> 00:05:30.623
vos iz geven di parnose funem ta- funem tatn?

00:05:30.087 --> 00:05:32.245
mayn foter iz geven

00:05:32.245 --> 00:05:35.701
a KABLAN unternemer fun glezeray

00:05:36.245 --> 00:05:37.824
un maleray.

00:05:37.824 --> 00:05:39.964
merstnteyl hot er gearbet in

00:05:39.964 --> 00:05:43.070
poylishe institutn

00:05:43.070 --> 00:05:45.806
vayl loyt zayn familye

00:05:45.806 --> 00:05:48.829
loyt zayn nomen hot men gemeynt er iz a krist.

00:05:48.804 --> 00:05:49.428
aha.

00:05:49.666 --> 00:05:53.333
efsher dos iz geven di

00:05:53.333 --> 00:05:56.859
un di muter iz geven a shtubike froy.

00:05:56.482 --> 00:05:58.279
vi azoy hot geheysn di ma, di mame?

00:05:58.105 --> 00:05:59.280
Gite.

00:05:59.269 --> 00:05:59.928
Gite.

00:05:59.982 --> 00:06:00.982
KEN.

00:06:01.101 --> 00:06:02.977
in der heym hot men geredt poylish?

00:06:02.964 --> 00:06:03.789
yidish.

00:06:03.817 --> 00:06:04.499
yidish.

00:06:04.543 --> 00:06:07.385
ikh hob geendikt a poylishe shul.

