yo, ir zent gegangen mit im, zogt ir, in, sport, vos gedenkt ir?

00:06:14.175 --> 00:06:15.762
KEN. er iz geven

00:06:15.981 --> 00:06:20.174
zeyer a sheyner mentsh un a guter mentsh.

00:06:20.174 --> 00:06:22.525
un az ikh fleg darfn vos koyfn

00:06:22.525 --> 00:06:24.455
fleg ikh geyn mitn foter

00:06:24.455 --> 00:06:25.841
vayl ikh fleg

00:06:25.841 --> 00:06:27.402
mer gevinen

00:06:27.402 --> 00:06:28.754
vi mit di muter.

00:06:28.734 --> 00:06:29.696
yo.

00:06:29.526 --> 00:06:32.877
er iz geven a shtiler mentsh.

00:06:32.877 --> 00:06:36.491
